      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know about the numbers, i've seen them a million times. it doesn't change the fact that my whole world is just empty. i look at my bed and it's just... huge and quiet and i just feel so incredibly worthless. like i'm just an inconvenience to everyone now that she's gone. it just feels like there's no way to make the heavy feeling stop. it just stays there, crushing me.",
